  fhir:description [ fhir:v "A formally or informally recognized grouping of organizations formed for the purpose of achieving some form of collective action. Includes institutions, departments etc\n\nOrganization represents Hospital and Departments configured in ARIA. A Hospital can have multiple departments.\n\nHospital is represented with category 'prov (Provider)' and Department is represented with category 'dept (Department)'. \n\nHospital and Department relationship is represented on Department."] ; # 
